    "description": "<strong>Synopsis</strong><br><i>&quot;Chain of karma&quot;</i><br><br>Ivan Vinogradov is the victim of a top-secret project that was executed by CIA.<br><br>He was on the verge of death after the project was abruptly aborted, but is rescued by a CIA agent named Frank Connery.<br>For some reason, Frank helps Ivan in various ways.<br><br>Ivan lives with nightmares every night because of what he went through in the facility.<br>The only thing that sooths his pain is the unknown drug he has been using since the project.<br>However, when the medicine is running low, Ivan wanders through the night to find a replacement.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>- Top Down Shooting Action Game with Graphic Novel Style <br>- Simple, intuitive controls <br>- Gamepad Support <br>- Hundreds of high-quality pre-rendered cutscenes <br>- Classical music by Chopin, Mussorgsky, Liszt, and a variety of original soundtracks<br><br><br><br>※EPISODE 1 consists of 5 chapters.<br>※Furies &amp; Magazines is planned up to EPISODE 7.",
